ratings.en: Koi ga Shitai Kakkoii kedo Yurusenai!
Kisu no kouishyou aitsu no kimochi ga wakaranai
Futatsu no kisu Yuu ni koibito ga ita!?
Ginta no kokuhaku Omae wo aitsu ni watasanai!
Koibito no densetsu Medaiyu ni omoi wo komete
Koi no Hokkaidou Dounatteruno? Ano futari!
Otona no kaori Yakimochi nante yaitenai!
Arubaito Koi no shoubu wa uriage shidai!
Hajimete no yoru Ofuro de doki
